title: Corporate Life v1.0 mod
description:
Only you can make the best decisions as you move from an aspiring college student to a high flying boardroom executive as you face hundreds of challenging scenarios.

Do you outwit your company's competitors and outsmart your colleagues or do you focus on a work life balance and work cooperatively? 

Dictate the outcome of your Corporate Life as you juggle the competing interests of your health, finances, social life, career aspirations, reputation and emotion. 

Make the right call and watch as you enjoy the fruits of life or take a wrong turn and agonise in despair. Win the keys to the city, excel in all parameters or wind up in jail as you do whatever it takes to make it to the top.
